# basic-demo.tape
# A minimal VHS recording showing basic commands

# Output
Output basic-demo.gif

# Configuration
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set FontSize 32
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 40
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

# Main Recording
Type "# Welcome to VHS!"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "echo 'Hello from VHS terminal recording'"
Enter
Wait
Sleep 2s

Type "ls -la"
Enter
Wait
Sleep 2s

Type "# That's it - easy!"
Enter
Sleep 2s
